        <item>
            <title>刘德华现身华为 Mate XT 非凡大师宣传片　全球首个三折叠手机登场</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/05/huawei-matext-andylau/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=huawei-matext-andylau</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/05/huawei-matext-andylau/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Ngan Ivan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 09:00:21 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提电话]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Huawei]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Huawei Mate XT]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Mate XT]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[刘德华]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[华为]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1260993</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">华为今日正式发布非凡大师品牌全新三折叠式手机 Mate XT 宣传片，品牌大使刘德华更出现在宣传片中并手持 Mate XT 为其首次公开真身。Mate XT 是全球首个三折叠式手机，预料会是 9 月 10 日举行「华为见非凡品牌盛典及鸿蒙智行新品发布会」的主角。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_30407"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/nG47VNO9ySE?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p style="font-weight: 400;">Mate XT 采用了「内折 + 外折 + 双铰链」的设计，从宣传片中可以看到 Mate XT 完全展开后的屏幕非常巨大，大约为 10 吋。Mate XT 在厚度控制上的表现同样相当出色，展开后的屏幕厚度预计不超过 5 mm。手机的背部与 Mate 60 RS 非凡大师相似，采用了八角形的镜头模组，当中还有一个方形的潜望式长焦镜头。背部使用了素皮材质，底部印有华为和 ULTIMATE DESIGN（非凡大师）品牌的标志。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1261044 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/matext1img-694x298.jpg" alt="Mate XT" width="694" height="298" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/matext1img-694x298.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/matext1img.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1261042 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/matextdesign-694x390.jpg" alt="Mate XT" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/matextdesign-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/matextdesign.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">图片来源：<a href="https://www.huaweicentral.com/here-is-the-first-official-look-at-huawei-mate-xt-tri-fold-phone/">Huawei Central</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">华为常务董事兼终端 BG 董事长余承东早前表示华为接下来推出的这一代折叠式手机，是别人想得到但做不到的产品。华为团队为了 Mate XT 概念的构想已长达 5 年有多，如今终于可以量产并面世。</p><p>资料及图片来源：<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/u/1839167003?luicode=10000011&amp;lfid=1005051839167003">微博 @华为终端</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/11/huawei-matebook-x-pro-review-2/review-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【评测】Huawei MateBook X Pro　外形　手感　屏幕　键盘　功能　效能开箱评测</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/04/stability-issues-hold-back-huawei-ai-chips-to-outpace-nvidia-report/ai/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">华为 AI 晶片难取代 Nvidia　中国企业指 Ascend 晶片不稳定又慢</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/02/huawei-29/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">华为撞 Apple 于同一日举行发布会，余承东：将发布华为巅峰之作</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/05/huawei-matext-andylau/mobile-phone/">刘德华现身华为 Mate XT 非凡大师宣传片　全球首个三折叠手机登场</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
