        <item>
            <title>淘宝天猫将支援微信支付   9 月陆续分批开放用户使用</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/05/taobao-wechatpay/life-tech/epayment/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=taobao-wechatpay</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/05/taobao-wechatpay/life-tech/epayment/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Ngan Ivan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 07:00:23 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[智慧城市]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[社交网络]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[买物情报]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[电子支付]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[wechat pay]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[微信支付]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[淘宝]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1260962</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">淘宝早在年初便已经有用户发现，部分淘宝订单的支付页面出现「微信支付」的选项，可以转至「微信支付」进行付款。当时已经有淘宝计划全面支援「微信支付」服务的消息。最近淘宝和天猫分别发出公告计划新增「微信支付」服务，目前已向部分商家发出邀请试用，签约后即可开通「微信支付」。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1260968 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/kcoss1725433350355-694x307.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="307" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/kcoss1725433350355-694x307.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/kcoss1725433350355.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1260972 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/123-694x433.jpg" alt="淘宝" width="694" height="433" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/123-694x433.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/123.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">图片来源：<a href="https://helpcenter.taobao.com/servicehall/knowledge_detail?kwdContentId=543618262673589248&amp;spm=service_hall.25034535.shcLibrary_lcork9x3.543618262673589248&amp;hcSessionId=3-1281-fa798edf-2618-47b4-b845-27acacb81bfe#1000113210,1000113484,,">淘宝</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">阿里巴巴旗下淘宝和天猫发出意见征集，指为提升消费者的购物体验正计划新增「微信支付」服务。目前淘宝已经向部分商家发出试用的邀请，而在淘宝的商家服务大厅中也能发现「微信支付」的一系列使用指南。商家签约完成开通「微信支付」服务后，消费者在对应的店舖便能使用「微信支付」进行付款。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1260975 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/kcoss17254083985812-325x580.jpeg" alt="" width="325" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/kcoss17254083985812-325x580.jpeg 325w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/kcoss17254083985812.jpeg 364w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 325px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">图片来源：<a href="https://helpcenter.taobao.com/servicehall/knowledge_detail?kwdContentId=543618262673589248&amp;spm=service_hall.25034535.shcLibrary_lcork9x3.543618262673589248&amp;hcSessionId=3-1281-fa798edf-2618-47b4-b845-27acacb81bfe#1000113210,1000113484,,">淘宝</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">淘宝表示目前「微信支付」服务仅向部分商家发出邀请，而未有收到邀请的商家亦无需焦急，预料 9 月中旬会分批给更多商家加入开通「微信支付」服务的计划。其实一直有淘宝开通「微信支付」的呼声，其竞争对手「拼多多」很早之前便已经有「微信支付」的服务，早前市值更一度超越阿里巴巴。如今淘宝开通「微信支付」相信有助改善购物体验，方便用户的使用同样能吸引更多新用户，增强竞争力。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">资料来源：<a href="https://app.xinhuanet.com/news/article.html?articleId=a811ef63-298b-4185-8806-282dc65ccebf&amp;fbclid=IwY2xjawFGC3FleHRuA2FlbQIxMAABHaXbXGCcVbI0J_bHfR3HMwpkNj_7BlTFocuXhpmGcxK-F9YdfrpXSmFbbw_aem_uM3myJE8KJLRCInt3cMS-w">新华网</a></p><p>图片来源：<a href="https://www.cbndata.com/information/222386">CBNData</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/26/taobao-xiaomi-vision-pro-trial-su7-car/vr-mr-ar/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">安坐家中 Vision Pro 云端试车　淘宝小米合作推虚拟小米 SU7 试车体验</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/07/octopus-wechatpayhk-taxi/life-tech/epayment/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">香港的士增设微信支付，加入至八达通支付网络</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/25/taobao-campaign-free-delivery-worldwide/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">淘宝推全球包邮计划，港澳台等亚洲地区率先提供</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/05/taobao-wechatpay/life-tech/epayment/">淘宝天猫将支援微信支付   9 月陆续分批开放用户使用</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
